Package com.nnk.poseidon.controller

Class RuleNameController

java.lang.Object
com.nnk.poseidon.controller.RuleNameController
@Controller public class RuleNameController extends Object
A class that receives requests made from some of the usual CRUD endpoints and specific URL for the RuleNames. As the methods return views, @Controller is used instead of @RestController. Indeed, the response doesn't have to be serialized via @ResponseBody
